{"tid":1651183,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（檢討post)講下今日18區開花問題","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T09:18:24.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1d9d4aade7431e22526a5a1a199a7a2ef5c408","tid":1651183,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"其實事前，有幾個問題<br />\n宣傳不足<br />\n一區幾個集合點<br />\n又一點二點三點<br />\n不過呢個我覺得唔係主要問題<br />\n<br />\n主要問題係魔警進化左：<br />\n<br />\n係連登mon post, tg, fb睇住晒，知道集合地點時間，就有晒事前針對性部置<br />\n有強国無限兵力支援，可以做到18區魔警開花<br />\n各個路口有便衣睇，人見到有人集就叫人來清<br />\n主要街道有大量魔警守住<br />\n一有人集，就清<br />\n有伏兵係黨鐵，360之類<br />\n見人就拉，等你驚，等你集唔到<br />\n當然魔警混入呢d基本野實有<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔係集合定分散問題，係魔警有晒部署問題<br />\n有人話事前唔通知就得，唔事先通知集得多人？<br />\n<br />\n大家可以討論下點應對"},{"pid":"c0e8de3c2a22c4d296998a4fff62c4125b08abeb","tid":1651183,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"18區同時間開花, 只可以進行和理非活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651125</a>"},{"pid":"1d02931db3cc459982d867c218fbdff23139c489","tid":1651183,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144dbc2087c2fbe819225502890ddec785ab6896","tid":1651183,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0e8de3c2a22c4d296998a4fff62c4125b08abeb","tid":1651183,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"18區同時間開花, 只可以進行和理非活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651125</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"無可能，運動只可以越演越烈！"},{"pid":"bf75c60be787fe1d864ff523b0cc207278218a4b","tid":1651183,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"144dbc2087c2fbe819225502890ddec785ab6896","tid":1651183,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0